radiographic_examinations.findings: Clear lower chest; liver, gallbladder, spleen, adrenal glands, pancreas are all within normal limits. Kidneys are normal aside from a tiny sub-cm hypodensity in the right kidney likely a renal cyst. Appendix measures 11 mm at proximal portion with hyperemic thickened wall and subtle fat stranding. Postpartum uterus with enlarged endometrial canal containing fluid. No adnexal pathology identified. Lymphadenopathy present.
